According to Captain Stanley Magaela, the police found Ms Phochana in the bathtub with multiple stab wounds. A knife was also found under the bathtub. “Her son, Eric Phochana (28), was arrested shortly after in connection with her murder,” said Capt. Magaela. Mr Phochana appeared in the Groblersdal Magistrates’ Court on Monday. The case was postponed to February 16 for a formal bail application. • Ms Phochana was newly elected as a Ward Committee member on January 20.